column2: SELECT f.plateifu, t.mangaid, f.objra, f.objdec, f.REDSHIFT,  f.PHOTOMETRIC_MASS, t.nsa_petro_th5#,  nsa_elpetro_absmag_u, nsa_elpetro_absmag_g, nsa_elpetro_absmag_r, nsa_elpetro_absmag_i, nsa_elpetro_absmag_z FROM mangatarget as t   JOIN mangaFirefly as f ON f.mangaID = t.MANGAID WHERE MANGA_TARGET3 = #  and nsa_elpetro_mass > #
